{"tid":2328842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"避免傷害「玩家感情」？GOG 平台遭抗議後下架《還願》商品頁面","createTime":"2020-12-16T21:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T07:14:28.000Z","uid":312169,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8da4a89921bdde91dd322ffe214294fcb6f5462a","tid":2328842,"uid":312169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:39:57.000Z","msg":"赤燭遊戲於 12 月 16 日宣布，旗下研發心靈恐怖遊戲《還願》PC 版將於 12 月 18 日在 GOG 平台重新上市，然而消息公布不到 6 小時卻突然生變，GOG 平台稍早緊急撤下商品頁面，並發公告表示「這款遊戲將不會在 GOG 平台上架」。<br />\n<br />\n《還願》2019 年 2 月上市後曾因為被發現遊戲中符咒埋梗，而引發中國玩家不滿，導致遊戲發行商決定終止合作並將《還願》暫時下架。7 月開發團隊曾談到此事造成的傷害，並確認《還願》短期內將不會重新上架，未來將視情況再認真評估《還願》重新上線的可能性。今年 6 月赤燭遊戲在台推出《還願》台灣限定實體版，更於昨日宣布決定於 12 月 18 日在 GOG 平台重新上市 PC 數位版本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://GOG.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGOG.com&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=5d3d1fd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">GOG.com</a> 是一家電玩遊戲和電影的數位發行平台，母公司為 CD Projekt，總部位於波蘭華沙，透過無數位版權管理（DRM-free）的方式販賣遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n　　然而，昨日晚間此消息曝光後，大量中國玩家前往 GoG 中國微博帳號提出質疑，更揚言抵制同樣為 CD Projekt 集團出品的《電馭叛客 2077（中國譯作「賽博朋克 2077」）》。對此，GoG 官方微博先是發表了「<a href=\"http://GOG.COM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGOG.COM&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=c082c621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">GOG.COM</a> 保證不會做出傷害大家感情的事情，請大家放心」之後刪除此一貼文。隨後，GoG 又透過官方微博以及國際版推特帳號正式宣布，《還願》將不會在 GOG 平台上架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzEQf6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzEQf6R.jpg&h=46668001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://GOG.COM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGOG.COM&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=c082c621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">GOG.COM</a> (@GOGcom) Tweeted:<br />\nEarlier today, it was announced that the game Devotion is coming to GOG. After receiving many messages from gamers, we have decided not to list the game in our store. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GOGcom/status/1339227388438306817?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGOGcom%2Fstatus%2F1339227388438306817%3Fs%3D20&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=7df66c90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGOGcom%2Fstatus%2F1339227388438306817%3Fs%3D20&h=95a21845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GOGcom/status/1339227388438306817?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n source: <a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=208029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D208029&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=5b605272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=208029</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncyberpunk2077個故事背景大家知㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔知睇依度: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2321689/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2321689/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫下手，幫CD project同中國玩家解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.12377.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.12377.cn%2F&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=5a76431c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.12377.cn/</a>"},{"pid":"0aa767517dbaf209896921849456b54d93b6bf84","tid":2328842,"uid":312169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdfdb009d8157f1393864938cb16b86da9d0c48","tid":2328842,"uid":312169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94565f53af3a3ab98fcfc99c27ac461d097d613c","tid":2328842,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cbb6d39f6c9964a1adbc0bae0d690d1bef18b0","tid":2328842,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T23:03:05.000Z","msg":"更揚言抵制同樣為 CD Projekt 集團出品的《電馭叛客 2077（中國譯作「賽博朋克 2077」）》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前隻2077有台獨成份都唔敢出聲，宜家發現隻驚多bug唔好玩之後就做返愛国小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d1a7c871fa9ca92bd8cc7420a1e9a6288c579b","tid":2328842,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2eb1f4a08a6d56676c9f58db353d0d0a8062e49","tid":2328842,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"retweet新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1339394996731047940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1339394996731047940&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=0d9bd0a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK%2Fstatus%2F1339394996731047940&h=5628c135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK/status/1339394996731047940</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/winandmachk/status/1339379729208623106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwinandmachk%2Fstatus%2F1339379729208623106&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE14L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=ac8491a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwinandmachk%2Fstatus%2F1339379729208623106&h=25ff772a\" data-a